snippet.title: First day of Amy Coney Barrett’s Supreme Court confirmation hearing - 10/12 (FULL LIVE STREAM)
snippet.description:
The Senate Judiciary Committee will begin hearing testimony on Oct. 12 as part of Judge Amy Coney Barrett’s Supreme Court confirmation. The Post’s Libby Casey will anchor live, uninterrupted coverage and be joined by reporters Emma Brown, Aaron Blake, Rhonda Colvin and Karoun Demirjian for analysis on day one of the hearing. Read more: https://wapo.st/2IaoDd3. Subscribe to The Washington Post on YouTube: https://wapo.st/2QOdcqK
